item.title: CVE-2022-4399|2024-08-03T01:41:44.420Z -- ticklishhoneybee -- nodau
item.description: A vulnerability was found in TicklishHoneyBee nodau. It has been rated as critical. Affected by this issue is some unknown functionality of the file src/db.c. The manipulation of the argument value/name leads to sql injection. The name of the patch is 7a7d737a3929f335b9717ddbd31db91151b69ad2. It is recommended to apply a patch to fix this issue. The identifier of this vulnerability is VDB-215252.
